billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

title: Creates the seed-NY investment fund
summary: Creates the seed-NY investment fund; authorizes the transfer of all assets and liabilities of the small business technology investment fund for the Seed-NY investment fund.
lawSection: New York State Urban Development Corporation Act
actClause: AN ACT to amend the New York state urban development corporation act and the public authorities law, in relation to creating the seed-NY investment fund
